channel.title: Could i be rich or atleast some money?
channel.description:
OK yesterday i was helping on renovating my great grandma's kitchen and i found an old "Yale" standard skeleton key. So i went on E bay and tried to look it up, No search results found. Then i looked up "Yale skeleton key" and i got a bunch of old looking ones from the search but nothing like mine. they all have only 2 teeth, this key is old and looks like a standard day key but double sided and rusty. If you want I can post a picture later but now I need to look more. So if anyone could help let me know.
EDIT: uploaded pic [IMG]http://i238.photobucket.com/albums/ff14/vexx1345/key.png[/img] sorry for bad quality camera is dead so i used webcam and prnt screen if you look closely you can see the teeth on both sides
